'''''Chronic Illness''''' is a quarterly [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[medical journal]] that covers research in the field of [[chronic illness]]es. Its [[editor-in-chief]] is Christopher Dowrick ([[University of Liverpool]]). It was established in 2005 and is currently published by [[SAGE Publications]].

== Abstracting and indexing ==
''Chronic Illness'' is abstracted and indexed in:
:* [[British Nursing Index]]
:* [[EMBASE]]/[[Excerpta Medica]]
:* [[EmCare]]
:* [[SciVal]]
:* [[Scopus]]

